{
  "info": {
    "name": "Pawffy Vendor API",
    "_postman_id": "pawffy-vendor-2026",
    "description": "Vendor / Partner app backend — {{baseUrl}}\n\n## Flow\n1. Auth → Register / Login (role: partner)\n2. Onboarding → Business → Services → Availability → Documents → Review → Submit\n3. Admin verifies application\n4. Main app → Home, Requests, Calendar, Chats, Profile\n\n## Auth\nBearer JWT required on all `/api/vendor/*` routes.\nRegister/Login auto-save `token` and `userId`.\n\n## Roles\n- partner — vendor app endpoints\n- admin — review pending applications\n\n## Password policy\nMin 8 chars · uppercase + lowercase + digit\n\n## Auto variables\ntoken · adminToken · userId · businessId · serviceId · documentId · requestId · blockedDateId · conversationId · receiverId",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5001", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "businessId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "serviceId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "documentId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "requestId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "blockedDateId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "conversationId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "receiverId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "vendorEmail", "value": "vendor@pawffy.test", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "vendorPassword", "value": "Password1", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Auth",
      "description": "Vendor register & login. Saves token automatically.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Vendor",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data && r.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', r.data.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', r.data.user.id);",
                  "  console.log('Token & userId saved');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Amit Patel\",\n  \"email\": \"{{vendorEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{vendorPassword}}\",\n  \"acceptTerms\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/vendor/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "vendor", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Create partner account + draft business profile.\nRequires acceptTerms: true."
          }
        },
